<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.2">
<l>kaṉṟuka ḷōṭac ceviyiṟ kaṭṭeṟum pupiṭit tiṭṭāl</l>
<l>teṉṟik keṭumākil veṇṇey tiraṭṭi viḻuṅkumā kāṇpaṉ</l>
<l>niṉṟa marāmarañ cāyttāy nīpiṟan tatiru vōṇa</l>
<l>miṉṟunī nīrāṭa vēṇṭu mempirā ṉōṭātē vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [you] catch big black ants to put in the ears of the calves</l>
<l>so that they run away, if [they] are scattered and hurt,</l>
<l>let’s see how [you] collect and gulp down butter [then].</l>
<l>You who bent the enduring cadamba tree,</l>
<l>today is holy ōṇam, [when] you were born,</l>
<l>you must bathe in water! Our Lord, come, don’t run away!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
